        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 5 at 4:58PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 458 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Marfa Municipal Airport, or near Marfa, moving southwest at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts of 50 to 55 mph and half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Marfa and Marfa Municipal Airport.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
